<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="idc27b536b-47c4-11f1-bf59-9680b1269b87" identifier="/us/usc/t38/s315"><num value="315">§ 315.</num><heading> Regional offices</heading><subsection style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0" id="idc27b536c-47c4-11f1-bf59-9680b1269b87" identifier="/us/usc/t38/s315/a"><num value="a">(a)</num><content> The Secretary may establish such regional offices and such other field offices within the United States, its Territories, Commonwealths, and possessions, as the Secretary considers necessary.</content>
</subsection>
<subsection style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0" id="idc27dc36d-47c4-11f1-bf59-9680b1269b87" identifier="/us/usc/t38/s315/b"><num value="b">(b)</num><content> The Secretary may maintain a regional office in the Republic of the Philippines until <date date="2026-09-30">September 30, 2026</date>.</content>
</subsection>
